OL,3,CSNP pledges 'bold action to support
OL,4,Cfamilies' ` Mairi McAllan
OL,6,FThe SNP would demand increases in
OL,7,Fmaternity pay and longer shared
OL,8,Fparental leave as part of "bold action
OL,9,Fto support families", a cabinet
OL,10,Fminister has said.
OL,12,FSpeaking ahead of a visit to a parent
OL,13,Fand baby group in Midlothian in
OL,14,FThursday, Mairi McAllan, Cabinet
OL,15,FSecretary for Net Zero and Energy,
OL,16,Fsaid that parental leave entitlement
OL,17,Fin the UK currently lags "far behind"
OL,18,Fthat in other European countries.
