OL,3,CSNP pledges 'bold action to support
OL,4,Cfamilies' ` Mairi McAllan
OL,6,FShe said her party had a "bold vision"
OL,7,Ffor the country which "values parents'
OL,8,Ftime to bond with their baby".
OL,10,FThe party's manifesto, which was
OL,11,Fpublished on Wednesday, sets out a
OL,12,Fcommitment to increase paid maternity
OL,13,Fleave to one year, and to set
OL,14,Fmaternity pay at 100% of average
OL,15,Fweekly earnings for the first 12 weeks.
OL,17,FIt also includes a commitment to
OL,18,Fextend shared parental leave from 52
OL,19,Fto 64 weeks.
