OL,3,CSNP pledges 'bold action to support
OL,4,Cfamilies' ` Mairi McAllan
OL,6,FMs McAllan said: "The SNP's bold
OL,7,Fvision for Scotland values parents'
OL,8,Ftime to bond with their baby in the
OL,9,Fcrucial early stages of development.
OL,11,F"For too long, families have been
OL,12,Fshort-changed by Westminster with
OL,13,Fparental leave entitlement that trails
OL,14,Ffar behind our European neighbours.
OL,16,F"At this election, neither Labour nor
OL,17,Fthe Tories will take bold action to
OL,18,Fsupport families.
