OL,3,CSNP pledges 'bold action to support
OL,4,Cfamilies' ` Mairi McAllan
OL,6,F"The SNP are supporting families and
OL,7,Fthe people of Scotland through every
OL,8,Fstage of life, with the Baby Box, the
OL,9,FScottish Child Payment, free tuition,
OL,10,Ffree childcare, free prescriptions and
OL,11,Ffree personal care.
OL,13,F"With the full powers of independence,
OL,14,FScotland can go further and the people
OL,15,Fthat live here will make decisions
OL,16,Fabout Scotland.
OL,18,F"Vote SNP on 4th July for a future
OL,19,Fmade in Scotland, for Scotland."
